data.title: Sarah Ann Kennedy - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Sarah Ann Kennedy: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Actress, entertainer, artist, performer, screenwriter, and writer who is best known for voicing the character of Miss Rabbit in Peppa Pig. She has also worked as a writer for several television and film projects including Peppa Pig, EastEnders, and Last Days.

Before Fame

She worked as an animation lecturer at the University of Central Lancashire.

Trivia

She developed, wrote and directed her own series called Crapston Villas. It won awards including the Independent TV Award for Best Newcomer, and Broadcast Best Animation. She voiced Nanny Plum in Ben and Holly's Little Kingdom and Dolly in Pond Life.

Family Life

She married Rob Parr.
